                <div class="ProfileSidebar ProfileSidebar--withLeftAlignment">
  <div class="ProfileHeaderCard">
  <h1 class="ProfileHeaderCard-name">
    <a href="/fredgrindrod" class="ProfileHeaderCard-nameLink u-textInheritColor js-nav">Fred Grindrod</a>
  </h1>

  <h2 class="ProfileHeaderCard-screenname u-inlineBlock u-dir" dir="ltr">
    <a class="ProfileHeaderCard-screennameLink u-linkComplex js-nav" href="/fredgrindrod">
      <span class="username u-dir" dir="ltr">@<b class="u-linkComplex-target">fredgrindrod</b></span>
    </a>
  </h2>

  

      <p class="ProfileHeaderCard-bio u-dir" dir="ltr">Labour candidate for Bournville and Cotteridge. Former Parliamentary Candidate, Trade Unionist, Labour Party Activist, various other things.</p>

      <div class="ProfileHeaderCard-location ">
        <span class="Icon Icon--geo Icon--medium" aria-hidden="true" role="presentation"></span>
        <span class="ProfileHeaderCard-locationText u-dir" dir="ltr">
              Birmingham, England

        </span>
      </div>

      <div class="ProfileHeaderCard-url ">
        <span class="Icon Icon--url Icon--medium" aria-hidden="true" role="presentation"></span>
        <span class="ProfileHeaderCard-urlText u-dir">  <a class="u-textUserColor" target="_blank" rel="me nofollow noopener" href="https://t.co/7W0xUXUIKp" title="https://bournville-labour.org.uk">
    bournville-labour.org.uk
  </a>

</span>
      </div>


      <div class="ProfileHeaderCard-joinDate">
        <span class="Icon Icon--calendar Icon--medium" aria-hidden="true" role="presentation"></span>

  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="0"><a href="/hashtag/Birmingham?src=hash" data-query-source="hashtag_click" class="twitter-hashtag pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr"><s>#</s><b>Birmingham</b></a> <a href="/hashtag/Labour?src=hash" data-query-source="hashtag_click" class="twitter-hashtag pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr"><s>#</s><b>Labour</b></a>'s Manifesto for <a href="/hashtag/3May2018?src=hash" data-query-source="hashtag_click" class="twitter-hashtag pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr"><s>#</s><b>3May2018</b></a> offers <a href="/hashtag/hope?src=hash" data-query-source="hashtag_click" class="twitter-hashtag pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr"><s>#</s><b>hope</b></a> <a href="/hashtag/forthemany?src=hash" data-query-source="hashtag_click" class="twitter-hashtag pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr"><s>#</s><b>forthemany</b></a>. It's an ambitious plan for <a href="/hashtag/MunicipalSocialism?src=hash" data-query-source="hashtag_click" class="twitter-hashtag pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr"><s>#</s><b>MunicipalSocialism</b></a>. We'll build council houses, ensure young people have the skills they need to get good jobs, protect our most vulnerable &amp; restore civic pride in our great city.<a href="https://t.co/RWQVjyrrya" class="twitter-timeline-link u-hidden" data-pre-embedded="true" dir="ltr">pic.twitter.com/RWQVjyrrya</a></p>

      <li class="embed-link js-actionEmbedTweet" data-nav="embed_tweet">
        <button type="button" class="dropdown-link">Embed Tweet</button>
      </li>
  </ul>
</div>

</div>

  </div>

      </div>

  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="0">Great start to our Super Saturday campaign launch for local elections on 3 May.   <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="0">On <a href="/hashtag/InternationalWomensDay?src=hash" data-query-source="hashtag_click" class="twitter-hashtag pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr"><s>#</s><b>InternationalWomensDay</b></a> we remember women across the world who fight for equality. Campaigning recently with <a href="/LizClements" class="twitter-atreply pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr" data-mentioned-user-id="3651173116"><s>@</s><b>LizClements</b></a> &amp; <a href="/fredgrindrod" class="twitter-atreply pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr" data-mentioned-user-id="748818630930931713"><s>@</s><b>fredgrindrod</b></a> we remembered Julia Varley, trade unionist &amp; suffragette who set up branch of National Federation of Women Workers at local Cadbury Factory<a href="https://t.co/HfhNr5XL5C" class="twitter-timeline-link u-hidden" data-pre-embedded="true" dir="ltr">pic.twitter.com/HfhNr5XL5C</a></p>

  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="0">Today, the Tories and private train companies put up rail fares by 3.6%, the steepest hike in 5 years.

We were at <a href="/hashtag/Bournville?src=hash" data-query-source="hashtag_click" class="twitter-hashtag pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr"><s>#</s><b>Bournville</b></a> station this morning to protest the rip-off rises and share <a href="/UKLabour" class="twitter-atreply pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr" data-mentioned-user-id="14291684"><s>@</s><b>UKLabour</b></a>'s plans to bring railways back into public ownership <a href="/hashtag/RailFail?src=hash" data-query-source="hashtag_click" class="twitter-hashtag pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr"><s>#</s><b>RailFail</b></a><a href="https://t.co/UkwHYxSLDJ" class="twitter-timeline-link u-hidden" data-pre-embedded="true" dir="ltr">pic.twitter.com/UkwHYxSLDJ</a></p>

  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="0">Rail fares up by 3.4% &amp; season tickets by 3.6% tomorrow: another squeeze on living costs from the Tories. I'm at <a href="/hashtag/Bournville?src=hash" data-query-source="hashtag_click" class="twitter-hashtag pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr"><s>#</s><b>Bournville</b></a> station tomorrow with <a href="/marylockelabour" class="twitter-atreply pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr" data-mentioned-user-id="4872422746"><s>@</s><b>marylockelabour</b></a> <a href="/fredgrindrod" class="twitter-atreply pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr" data-mentioned-user-id="748818630930931713"><s>@</s><b>fredgrindrod</b></a> <a href="/BournvilleLab" class="twitter-atreply pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr" data-mentioned-user-id="1638238614"><s>@</s><b>BournvilleLab</b></a>. If you can, spare us a moment to hear how <a href="/hashtag/Labour?src=hash" data-query-source="hashtag_click" class="twitter-hashtag pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr"><s>#</s><b>Labour</b></a> will make a difference!<a href="https://t.co/7Bawm88OpY" class="twitter-timeline-link u-hidden" data-pre-embedded="true" dir="ltr">pic.twitter.com/7Bawm88OpY</a></p>
</div>

<p class="u-hiddenVisually" aria-hidden="true" data-aria-label-part="3">Ed Miliband added,</p>

  if(window.ttft){
    window.ttft.recordMilestone('page', document.getElementById('swift-page-name').getAttribute('content'));
    window.ttft.recordMilestone('section', document.getElementById('swift-section-name').getAttribute('content'));
    window.ttft.recordMilestone('client_record_time', window.ttft.now());
  }
</script>
